    • Camp

      public Camp(String campID, CampInformation campinfo)
      Constructs a new Feedback with the specified user ID, camp ID, and content. The feedback ID is automatically generated and incremented for each new Feedback.
      Parameters:
      campID - The ID of the camp the feedback is associated with.
      campinfo - The CampInformation wrapper object for the supplied information.
